{"tid":400652,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"慢煮法蘭西鴨胸配車厘子汁","createTime":"2017-09-15T03:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T17:24:48.000Z","uid":22793,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56cf1deeb2bc74273486a294aecba383f04a315c","tid":400652,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T03:46:30.000Z","msg":"Hello 大家好，又係我同大家分享煮野樂趣。唔講咁多，去相。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/112838_b0faed9af0b19e5898bec53fc8144fbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F112838_b0faed9af0b19e5898bec53fc8144fbb.jpg&h=83eb81c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/112843_b2b3a69abd584dbca9ac7075450a33a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F112843_b2b3a69abd584dbca9ac7075450a33a8.jpg&h=66ddec81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要係啲肥膏上面𠝹井井，咁煎既時候啲出快啲，靚啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/113306_f22d543ba52ac3674e80c26c4ff0c792.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F113306_f22d543ba52ac3674e80c26c4ff0c792.jpg&h=f063dfc3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/113310_72a351396e81460f4e6cd7867bea3002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F113310_72a351396e81460f4e6cd7867bea3002.jpg&h=d15b59b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後用 thyme, garlic ,bay leaf 抽真空，58&deg;c慢煮40分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/113559_4dc53c3ae2b8fbc23ef4f140e7fdf78a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F113559_4dc53c3ae2b8fbc23ef4f140e7fdf78a.jpg&h=0e64788c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再煎到金黃色，入焗爐130&deg;c 10分鐘 再rest 10分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/113915_8acf7792a8cda46923069c5312aa2065.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F113915_8acf7792a8cda46923069c5312aa2065.jpg&h=732dd887&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/113919_d39eca3a9e8617721e29b146266b2ac3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F113919_d39eca3a9e8617721e29b146266b2ac3.jpg&h=5bc9cc0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/113923_c5032f127d5f6a4a9ff9c0d468a27288.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F113923_c5032f127d5f6a4a9ff9c0d468a27288.jpg&h=2c543c75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車厘子開2去籽、落小小水煮到林林地可以搵隻差篤爛佢，再調味<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/114605_9244197ef354922595f1b1e04dad6b4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F114605_9244197ef354922595f1b1e04dad6b4e.jpg&h=3c0a10e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完成，Bon app&eacute;tit"},{"pid":"fe5195f4799091b881cae94faa7c096062cf8347","tid":400652,"uid":54197,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T03:51:24.000Z","msg":"你擺碟好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc444918e6badbfba392902cd07706ee8f09c66","tid":400652,"uid":22793,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T03:54:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你擺碟好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb12c5877a6a06db5d6ed84b96ed12853357e46","tid":400652,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T03:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/f